    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1 across all five operating points with GCI below 2% and output comparison error within experimental uncertainty. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device as specified in the context of use.",
